results.name: Decimal expansion of a parking constant related to the asymptotic expected number of cars, assuming random car lengths.
reference: Steven R. Finch, Mathematical Constants, Cambridge University Press, 2003, Section 5.3 Renyi's parking constant, p. 279.
link: G. C. Greubel, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..5000
formula: (1-1/2^((sqrt(17)-1)/4))*sqrt(Pi)*GAMMA(sqrt(17)/2)/(GAMMA((sqrt(17)+1)/4)*GAMMA((sqrt(17)+3)/4)^2), where GAMMA is the Euler Gamma function.
results.author: _Jean-François Alcover_, Jun 02 2014
